                        <div class="quiz-option" data-correct="false">Leave your home when the eye of the storm arrives</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="result-message"></div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="quiz-question" id="question-3" style="display: none;">
                    <h4>3. What is the recommended action during an earthquake?</h4>
                    <div class="quiz-options">
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-correct="false">Run outside immediately</div>
